a has been a victim of intimate partner violence.</h2><h3>What can happen to one woman out of five - can also happen to you. But there is help.</h3><p>HELPCHAT <a href="index.html">www.haltdergewalt.at</a> offers anonymous and confidential help. HELPCHAT  is a virtual information center for women and girls who are experiencing violence in all forms – physical, psychological and sexual.</p><p><strong>From October 12, 2020</strong> the professional online-help and -advice is available <strong>every day from 4pm to 10pm</strong> for women and girls affected by violence. Several <a href="consultants.html">consultants</a> offer their help at these times. Register yourself with a “nickname” and define a password of your choice. Everything else you need to know will be explained to you by the consultants, also in German and Turkish.</p><p>Above all <a href="index.html">www.haltdergewalt.at</a> offers the opportunity to use this information center as a dialogue platform, to build support groups and to find information about the legal situation, institutions for the protection of victims and party women organisations via linklist.</p><p>Here you can find the <a href="behavioral-rules.html">rules of conduct</a> for Helpchat.</p><span class="lineBottom"></span></div><div class="col-lg-1"></div><div class="col-lg-5 sidebar"><h3>Helpful links</h3><div class="list-group"><a href="http://www.aoef.at/" target="_blank" title="Open link in new window/tab" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">Verein Autonome Österreichische Frauenhäuser</a><span class="sr-only"> | </span><a href="http://www.aoef.at/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=58&amp;Itemid=133" target="_blank" title="Open link in new window/tab" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">BUNDESGESETZ zum Schutz vor Gewalt</a><span class="sr-only"> | </span><a href="http://www.aoef.at/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=13&amp;Itemid=120" target="_blank" title="Open link in new wi